{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0001", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "heading", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "ALAIN'S SONG"}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0002", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b2"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0003", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b3"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "Moise was born in 1908 The first of nine to follow, He loved to doodle and to lead The rest would have to swallow."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0004", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b4"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "An entrepreneur was born in him; The only one of all the eight. He sold his goods and pumped his gas It showed he had some class."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0005", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b5"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "When years were lean he gave out credit And never did complain. When folks were late to pay their bills He was paid when harvest came."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0006", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b6"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "His yard was filled with his creations; Artistic was his bent. He even cut linoleum The size of which was spent."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0007", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b7"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0008", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b8"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "In 1909 Louis was born. It made his brother happy. Now two could be mischievious And make their mother snappy."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0009", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b9"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "Louis spent his summertimes On his Grandpa's ranch; Riding horses, breaking broncos, Driving them all ants."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0010", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 1, "source_element_ids": ["p001-b10"], "source_printed_page_number": 1, "source_printed_page_label": "1", "text_quote": "He was good at farming And raising cattle too, Aberdeen Angus was his choice It stuck to him like glue."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0011", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "In '63 he gave it up And moved to fairer land; The oldest cried their eyeballs out The youngest joined the band."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0012", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b2"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0013", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b3"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "Yvonne was tall and stately 1911 was her year. She has her father's red hair At telling stories she's a dear."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0014", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b4"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "The only one of all the eight The piano she did play It made her mother happy For she played it well, you know."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0015", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b5"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "Yvonne wrote many a letter Each embellished with some jokes No one could do this better Which brought laughter to her folks."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0016", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b6"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "The only one for many years To live on the West Coast. She helped Darlene get on her way Of that she sure can boast."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0017", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b7"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0018", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b8"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "Uncle Rolland we all knew Was red as red could be. He looked just like his father His character filled with glee."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0019", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 2, "source_element_ids": ["p002-b9"], "source_printed_page_number": 2, "source_printed_page_label": "2", "text_quote": "He always had a story Like the time he passed a flask It was Marcella's wedding; The Scope sure did not last."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0020", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "He named his calves as they were born, Governor, J.J., Star, He even used the Russian names Of players from afar."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0021", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b2"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "Twenty-two years driving school bus, He never missed a day. He joked around and teased the kids And joined right in their play."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0022", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b3"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0023", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b4"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "Marie Paule came after Rolland. She played with him a lot. They even called her \"tomboy\" When hockey was her lot."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0024", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b5"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "She was a gentle person, Soft spoken, quiet too. You had to be reserved like her To get to know her through."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0025", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b6"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "She also lived in Flin Flon Where they raised the Menzies crew, Seven Men and Women Who grew and grew and grew!"}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0026", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b7"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "Now that she's retired She has little time alone; From Nova Scotia to Vancouver She's always on the roam."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0027", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b8"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "REFRAIN: Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0028", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 3, "source_element_ids": ["p003-b9"], "source_printed_page_number": 3, "source_printed_page_label": "3", "text_quote": "Aunt Edithe was a good cook. We all remember well! She was just like her mother The rest of us could tell."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0029", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "Her garden was her pride and joy; Her plot had ample room. If bees were scarce to pollinate She'd always use her broom."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0030", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b2"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "She knew all songs on radio; She'd sing them as she worked. If problems came you'd never know She never let them lurk."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0031", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b3"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "Even when her back was bad She'd always joke around About her weight or something else It never got her down."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0032", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b4"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "REFRAIN Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0033", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b5"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "Berthe was nicknamed \"La Corneil\" Because of her black hair; She bore the name with dignity She came out very fair."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0034", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b6"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "She never took life seriously; She saw its funny side. Her humor and the tricks she played Reached others in her stride."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0035", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b7"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "They'd go to Texas every year To miss the Flin Flon storms And even there she'd lead her friends Trimming down their girlish forms."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0036", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b8"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "Root beer was her speciality It made the family cheer Now that bingo's taken over She still runs in high gear."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0037", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 4, "source_element_ids": ["p004-b9"], "source_printed_page_number": 4, "source_printed_page_label": "4", "text_quote": "REFRAIN Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0038", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "Paul was born in '21 The last of all the ten. He was short and dark like Louis But spoiled within the den."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0039", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b2"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "Like his brother Smokey, He was artistically inclined. His hands he used in many ways To shape ideas from his mind."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0040", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b3"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "He also moved to B.C. When his family was half grown. Kamloops was the town they chose And that was where they'd own."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0041", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b4"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "He taught me how to dance one year. I stepped all over his shoes. He laughed and said he'd polish them And make them just like new."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0042", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b5"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "REFRAIN Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0043", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b6"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "The eight that lived were quite a bunch They all had spendid spouses. Who followed them where'er they went And embellished all their houses."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0044", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b7"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "Verna, Clara, Pat, Yvonne, Angus, Gene, and Paul Aunt Reine and all their children Could fill Veillardville hall."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0045", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b8"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "God has blessed our family He's taken some away, To teach us all a lesson Life's but a shortened stay."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0046", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b9"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "So while we're here together. Let's sing and celebrate. Forgive each other all our hurts Get rid of any hate."}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0047", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 5, "source_element_ids": ["p005-b10"], "source_printed_page_number": 5, "source_printed_page_label": "5", "text_quote": "As we go along our way, Remember we're a clan We come from Alma and Henri So let's strike up the band!"}
{"schema_version": "doc_web_provenance_block_v1", "module_id": "build_chapter_html_v1", "run_id": "alain-companion-alains-song-doc-web-r1", "created_at": "2026-07-03T06:48:32.346203Z", "block_id": "blk-chapter-001-0048", "entry_id": "chapter-001", "block_kind": "paragraph", "source_page_number": 6, "source_element_ids": ["p006-b1"], "source_printed_page_number": 6, "source_printed_page_label": "6", "text_quote": "REFRAIN Alain's our family name And proud of it are we, For we are descendants Of Alma and Henri."}
